metadata.name: Dank Pixels
metadata.description: Collection of 4444 Hemp Seeds, All will grow into their own unique strain. From Blue Cheese to Blue Diesel. Who will have the Dankest Pixels? Dank Pixels will be the first kind of growing NFT. Each holder will recieve multiple NFTs depending on the state of their Plants at 4 stages of the NFT cycles life. In other words - holders will recieve 4 NFTs over the space of 6 months. For the first cycle Growth will be completely random and generated. For future cycles Holders will be able to interact will data on our website. The website will allow holders to buy or rent perks which will produce higher growth, resulting in possible rarer NFTS.
